      <title>Kauč “Get back” inspiriran Beatlesima</title>
      <link>https://www.jutarnji.hr/domidizajn/inspiracije/kauc-get-back-inspiriran-beatlesima/9089210/</link>
      <description>KAD JE UDOBNOST NA PRVOM MJESTU - Dizajneri Ludovica+Roberto Palomba u suradnji s talijanskom tvrtkom Poltrona Frau stvorili su novi komad namještaja inspiriranog Beatlesima. Njihov kauč “Get back” inspiriran je, naravno, istoimenom pjesmom, a naglasak je stavljen na udobnost. Riječ je o niskom namještaju, koji se može prilagoditi prostoru u koji dolazi. Cijena još nije poznata.</description>
      <content:encoded>&lt;p align="justify"&gt;Dizajneri &lt;a href="https://www.palombaserafini.com/en/ps-a" target="_blank"&gt;Ludovica+Roberto Palomba&lt;/a&gt; u suradnji s talijanskom tvrtkom &lt;a href="https://www.poltronafrau.com" target="_blank"&gt;Poltrona Frau&lt;/a&gt; stvorili su novi komad namještaja inspiriranog Beatlesima. Njihov kauč “Get back” inspiriran je, naravno, istoimenom pjesmom, a naglasak je stavljen na udobnost. Riječ je o niskom namještaju, koji se može prilagoditi prostoru u koji dolazi. Cijena još nije poznata.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-1.jpg" id="_7ea9bc88-4bd1-441f-b72e-bb00fa785a9d" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-1jpg/9331328/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-1.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-2.jpg" id="_94914199-346c-4ee4-a90b-92cc85d1009f" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-2jpg/9331331/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-2.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-4.jpg" id="_e0927498-5a28-42cd-b4d8-c9dd7fb1a553" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-4jpg/9331334/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-4.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-5.jpg" id="_d33d1e3f-a55a-4174-b10d-90a96f4a3605" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-5jpg/9331337/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-5.jpg" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-6.jpg" id="_53a8d6dd-7902-4651-b867-285256309840" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-6jpg/9331340/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-6.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-7.jpg" id="_d12ad338-d51d-4af8-ad13-3e02b4b363d2" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-7jpg/9331343/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-7.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-8.jpg" id="_36a4e7d2-2159-4865-80b7-b30bc6cb1dd2" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-8jpg/9331349/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-8.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-9.jpg" id="_c74c60fb-5d3d-4158-b2c5-abea720e071b" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-9jpg/9331352/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-9.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-10.jpg" id="_d2b1b05d-9bb8-4623-bb46-9c1912898ea4" src="https://www.jutarnji.hr/incoming/get-back-sofa-palomba-poltrona-frau-10jpg/9331355/binary/Get-Back-sofa-Palomba-Poltrona-Frau-10.jpg" width="200" /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Više informacija na: &lt;a href="https://www.poltronafrau.com/it" target="_blank"&gt;www.poltronafrau.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
